text: Mušović is a Serbo-Croatian surname. Notable people with the surname include: *Džemaludin Mušović (born 1944), Bosnian football manager *Zećira Mušović (born 1996), Swedish footballer *Lepa Lukić (née Mušović), Serbian singer ==See also== *Musović *Mušić Category:Bosnian-language surnames Category:Patronymic surnames Category:Serbian-language surnames
